- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses optimization algorithms applied to machine learning tasks, which falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses optimization algorithms applied to control the weights and breakpoints in time series data, which is a topic related to systems and control.
